<parts.title>Ad [Addendum] 53. Witt Library. P.B.I Drawings Box 6. 'Feast of St. Martin'. Good photo of drawing-Photo erroneously- in Musée Atger, Montpellier; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G.
